@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yajloj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(v0)
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.21 / v1 + 0.33) * 0.06))
    tmp = 0.02
    v2 = (v2 * wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.41)))
    v1 = wp.cos(0.38)
    v2 = ((tmp - wp.exp(v0 + 0.14)) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.24 * v1 + 0.56)))
    data[tid] = v0
